    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "### Describe the bug\n\nThe sdist package at PyPI (see https://pypi.org/project/Cython/#files) does not contain the `tox.ini` file.  Please add the file to sdist to make the downstream testing easier.  Thank you.\n\n### Code to reproduce the behaviour:\n\n_No response_\n\n### Expected behaviour\n\n_No response_\n\n### Environment\n\nCython version: 0.29.32\r\n\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_",
    "closed_at": "2023-01-05T14:54:41Z",
    "comment_data": [
        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Thanks, I've included the file for the next release.\r\n\r\nHowever, the most likely reason why it was missing from the sdist is that we aren't using it. Even the list of test envs was entirely outdated. We might end up removing the file rather than keeping it up to date.",
